text: 154 (one hundred fifty-four) is the natural number after 153 and before 155. == Mathematics == *154 is an even number. *It is a composite number, because it can be factored into smaller prime numbers. The prime factorization of 154 is 2×7×11. *The divisors of 154 are 1, 2, 7, 11, 14, 22, 77, and 154. == Other facts == *Sonnet 154 is the last sonnet written by William Shakespeare. *154 is the name of a 1979 music album by the English rock band Wire.
